# Primary User Flow

## Medicine Lookup Journey

```text
User Opens Platform
        ↓
User Enters Medicine Name
        ↓
System Validates Input
        ↓
Retrieve Medicine Record
        ↓
Check Drug Interactions
        ↓
Generate AI Response
        ↓
Apply Safety Constraints
        ↓
Display Structured Output
````

